data.description: BEACH LIFE IS CALLING YOU! SEE THE VIRTUAL TOUR UNDER PHOTOS. Nearly 2500 ft.² Located in serene & eclectic Flagler Beach. This 3 bed/ 3 bath home is just 2 blocks from the ocean & walking distance to the public boat ramp, the local favorite watering holes, restaurants, and night life. The open floor plan, features beach tones, luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout, spacious kitchen with granite counters & prep island. Oversized owner's suite highlighted by a jetted garden tub, separate shower and dual vanities. large spare bedrooms, one with a Murphy bed, huge great room with bay windows & gas fireplace , large sunroom , fenced rear yard. Solar powered assisted electricity with battery backup 2 car garage and boat pad
